            <p><strong>Question 4:</strong> Choose the word that is closest in meaning to "Ephemeral".</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution">
            <p><strong>Solution:</strong> The correct answer is "Short-lived".</p>
            <p>Explanation: "Ephemeral" means lasting for a very short time.</p>
